WEBVTT

00:03:30.091 --> 00:03:31.691
But now, it was closing.

00:03:33.064 --> 00:03:36.653
And the company
wasn't just giving up on yogurt,

00:03:37.445 --> 00:03:39.112
it was giving up on them.

00:03:40.191 --> 00:03:41.861
As if they were not good enough.

00:03:44.567 --> 00:03:48.131
And I was shocked
how these people were behaving.

00:03:49.177 --> 00:03:51.844
There was no anger, there were no tears.

00:03:53.059 --> 00:03:54.498
Just silence.

00:03:54.522 --> 00:03:57.455
With grace, they were
closing this factory.